# 🧠 OS Concept 1: Serverless Computing

## 1️⃣ Simple Idea

In serverless computing:

👉 developers write code
👉 cloud provider manages servers automatically

You don’t manage infrastructure manually.

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Ordering taxi 🚕 using app.

You use service,

but don’t manage vehicle maintenance.

---

## ⚙️ How It Works

Event occurs:

```text id="y8v2mp"
HTTP request
File upload
Database trigger
```

Cloud automatically runs function.

---

## Advantages

✔ automatic scaling
✔ lower operational effort
✔ pay only when used

---

## Disadvantages

❌ cold start latency
❌ less infrastructure control

---

## Examples

* Amazon Web Services Lambda
* Google Cloud Functions

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why serverless is scalable?**

👉 Because cloud automatically allocates resources based on demand.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="8m4zpk"
Write code, cloud handles servers
```

