# 🧠 OS Concept 2: Autoscaling Systems

🔥 Important cloud interview topic.

---

## 1️⃣ Simple Idea

System automatically increases or decreases resources based on load.

---

## Example

Traffic suddenly increases:

```text id="6x2qrd"
1 server → 5 servers
```

Automatically.

---

## Why Important?

✔ handles traffic spikes
✔ cost efficient
✔ improves availability

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Restaurant hiring extra staff during rush hours.

---

## 🔗 Connection

Often works with:

* load balancing
* cloud platforms

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why autoscaling useful?**

👉 It dynamically adjusts resources according to workload demand.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="2v7nkt"
More load → more resources
```

---

# ⚙️ COA Concept 3: Sparse Computation in AI

🔥 Advanced AI optimization concept.

---

## 1️⃣ Simple Idea

Many AI models contain lots of zero/unimportant values.

Sparse computation skips unnecessary calculations.

---

## Example

Instead of computing:

```text id="4k8qms"
0 × weight
```

Skip it.

---

## Why Useful?

✔ faster execution
✔ lower memory usage
✔ energy efficient

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Ignoring empty seats while counting passengers.

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why sparse computation improves AI efficiency?**

👉 Because unnecessary operations are skipped.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="9r5xvw"
Sparse = skip useless work
```

---

